            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "For people coming across this issue after nvim 0.11.1 which made `ESC` and `<C-[>` no longer equivalent - [that's intentional](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/33711). Just map both:\n\n```\n\" Enable <ESC> to go back to normal mode\ntnoremap <ESC> <C-\\><C-n>\ntnoremap <C-[> <C-\\><C-n>\n```",
